-- Q1: Product Category with Highest Sales

### ðŸ“„ SQL Query:

```sql
SELECT 
    [Product_Category],
    SUM(Sales) AS Total_Sales
FROM 
    [dbo].[DSA_KMS_Sql_Case_Study_Project]
GROUP BY 
    [Product_Category]
ORDER BY 
    SUM(Sales) DESC;
```

```sql
SELECT 
    [Product_Category],
    FORMAT(SUM(Sales), 'C', 'en-NG') AS Total_Sales_Naira
FROM 
    [dbo].[DSA_KMS_Sql_Case_Study_Project]
GROUP BY 
    [Product_Category]
ORDER BY 
    SUM(Sales) DESC;
```
